The 'Lilypad' project is an attempt to make a lightweight reusable
MVC framework for launching web applications. In addition to the MVC component
Lilypad also attempts to address building an extensible library of common code
shared across web applications.

Version 1 Goals
    - Create Class Autoloader functionality
    - Create basic application framework
    - Create basic Controller / Dispatcher
    - Create routes for controller / dispatcher


